node.text:
#AD Since it’s launch last year, I’ve been using @ArmaniBeauty #MyWay fragrance. 
It’s sweet, feminine scent is natural and perfect for all year round. 🌸 
The #MyWay bottle is not only elegant to look at, but also reflects a commitment to sustainability as its refill system, allows for less waste and encourages recycling! 
Now available at @bootsuk @ArmaniBeauty #ArmaniMyWay #ArmaniBeauty
